data.description: Stunning home in Pinon Creek just waiting for Spring to roll around! This property is an entertainers delight with its crystal clear pool and a therapeutic detached hot tub! This tree studded lot has several serene sitting areas for relaxing outdoors.  It offers 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths, 2 car garage on a beautiful corner lot so you'll only have 1 next-door neighbor. The 4th bedroom could be secondary living.  The homeowner spared no expense on the owned solar system, new roof was replaced last year and gutters installed. Every system has been meticulous maintained. The layout is centered around the kitchen - the heart of the home, where many memories are made! Ring door bell/camera, wine fridge, pot rack and all the items outside convey except the gas grill and smoker . You can't beat the proximity to Schools, all the shopping, restaurants and the Stoneoak medical center.  Don't miss out on this beauty!
